metadata.name: Degen Apocalypse #1
metadata.description: Together we rebuild Degentopia! Once a flourishing city, Degentopia was filled with investor, traders, artists, and degens. Then suddenly a bearish explosion overcame the paradise and left it in ruins. Those seeking for their oasis in the desert are known as the Degen Apocalypse. With over 150 hand-drawn pixel traits, each piece is a unique masterpiece that embodies the spirit of the Degentopia.
